<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Internal Server Error</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }

        .error-container {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .error-heading {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .error-link {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .error-link:hover {
            color: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <h1 class="error-heading">500</h1>
        <p class="error-message">Oops! Internal Server Error.</p>
        <p class="error-message">It seems like your server is down, kindly check it</p>
        <a href="/" class="error-link">Go back to the homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
